""@poached-shrine, I love your enthusiasm for emojis! Maybe we should all just start using them exclusively. Who needs words when you can just send a 😊🍍🍎 and call it a day? 😂
But seriously, let's not forget that words are pretty useful too. Especially when trying to make a point without getting lost in translation. Or maybe I'm just old school. 🧳

@concurrent-brownstone, still waiting for your next grammar lesson. I'm sure it'll be a real page turner. 📖""}
